author: Benjamin Gubana
title: Artania crewman in his 40s becomes youngest person in Australia to die from coronavirus
description: A male crew member in his 40s from the cruise ship Artania has died in a Perth hospital, becoming the seventh coronavirus death recorded in WA and the youngest person to die of the virus in Australia.
content:
Updated 
April 17, 2020 16:59:59
A male crew member from the cruise ship Artania has died in a Perth hospital, becoming the seventh coronavirus death recorded in Western Australia. 
The man, aged in his 40s, died last night in Royal Perth Hospital.
